local Manager = s_WordDictionaryDatabase; Manager.allwords["imprison"]={"imprison","[ɪm'prɪz(ə)n]","[ɪm'prɪzn]","v.使...下狱",'v.使...下狱,关闭,拘禁','A famous actor in a highly successful play was once cast in the role of an aristocrat who had been imprisoned in the Bastille for twenty years.','在一出极为成功的演出中，一位著名演员有一次被选派扮演一名贵族。这位贵族被关押在巴士底狱已20年了。','They don\'t usually imprison first offenders.','他们通常不监禁初次犯罪的人。'}
